1. EventBridge Schedule
aws events put-rule --name route53-monthly-summary-schedule --schedule-expression "cron(0 7 5 * ? *)" --region ap-southeast-1

2. Add a target Lambda function:
  aws events put-targets \
  --rule route53-monthly-summary-schedule \
  --targets "Id"="1","Arn"="arn:aws:lambda:ap-southeast-1:886679765175:function:route53-invoice-summary"

3. Add Lambda permission to allow EventBridge to invoke it:
   aws lambda add-permission \
  --function-name route53-invoice-summary \
  --statement-id allow-eventbridge-schedule \
  --action 'lambda:InvokeFunction' \
  --principal events.amazonaws.com \
  --source-arn arn:aws:events:ap-southeast-1:886679765175:rule/route53-monthly-summary-schedule
